Deep Tech Talent Initiative: Call for Training Proposals - Event series

Would you like to boost deep-tech education in Europe?

Join us on our event series and learn more about the call for training proposals with us.

EIT Digital Glasgow Summer School Information Session

The Generative AI Toolkit for Start-up and Scale-up Growth

We warmly invite you to attend our Information Session for Glasgow University Summer School which takes place as an online event on Thursday, May 9 from 12:00 to 13:15 CEST (11:00 to 12:15 BST).

April 17, 2024 · Brussels, Belgium & online

AI, Data and Robotics Association (ADRA) Information Day and Brokerage Event 2024

The AI, Data and Robotics Association (ADRA), in strategic collaboration with EIT Digital, the European Commission, Ideal-ist, and the network of National Contact Points for ICT research, invites you to participate in an Information Day and Brokerage Event for 2024. This event provides a platform to delve into upcoming funding opportunities within the amended Horizon Europe Cluster 4 'Digital, Industry and Space' Work Programme, the recently launched Digital Europe programme, and the EIC accelerator.
